c: 3
v: 45
t: "Nabiyow cus Atu wokkel masuginnito malayka Diggah maryamey Yalli isik tan Qangarat geytimu waa Awkay migaq kak masiic maryam Baxa Qiisay Addunyaay Akeeral kaxxa konnaba leeh Yallih xaqul Qhiyaamah Ayró Yalli xayyoysiteh yan marih loowot yanil koo Aytikumusa Yalli, teetik itte waqdi malayka"